Contributing

We welcome contributions to PyCUTEst, please create a pull request on our PyCUTEst GitHub repository where your contribution will be reviewed. For instructions on creating pull requests, please see the GitHub documentation. All pull requests will be automatically tested using GitHub’s continuous integration framework.
